<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>5.<sp/>update(chave,<sp/>nova\_descrição)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>6.<sp/>delete(chave)</highlight></codeline>
